snippet.title: Telepathy Zero Free (iPhone & iPad Game Review)
snippet.description:
Get it on App Store: http://bit.ly/1iyBFNF

Use your Psychic abilities to complete against the other test subjects and prove your telepathic powers! Use your otherworldly connections to determine the figure that will be shown. Each correct answer in a row will add to your streak, increasing your score and proving your psychic abilities for all to see!
